575
00:34:23,978 --> 00:34:25,980
-Geez.
-My goodness.

576
00:34:26,606 --> 00:34:28,149
I bought so many pretty things.

577
00:34:28,232 --> 00:34:29,734
Thank you so much.

578
00:34:29,817 --> 00:34:31,778
Mi-hwa, I had so much fun today.

579
00:34:31,861 --> 00:34:33,446
