600
00:35:52,108 --> 00:35:54,110
Please ask the forensics team for advice.

601
00:35:54,694 --> 00:35:56,362
-You can leave right after that.
-Yes, sir.

602
00:35:56,445 --> 00:35:58,281
I'll take care of this and go.

603
00:35:58,364 --> 00:35:59,240
All right.

604
00:36:08,791 --> 00:36:10,209
Yes, this is Detective Kim.

605
00:36:12,628 --> 00:36:13,921
