606
00:36:14,839 --> 00:36:16,007
Please go ahead.

607
00:36:16,090 --> 00:36:17,508
Min-ho.

608
00:36:19,677 --> 00:36:21,137
Did Min-ho come here?

609
00:36:21,220 --> 00:36:22,138
He didn't.

610
00:36:23,097 --> 00:36:24,307
He isn't anywhere.

611
00:36:24,390 --> 00:36:26,893
I went everywhere I thought he could be.

612
00:36:29,478 --> 00:36:32,815
I filed a report with the police,
so I'm sure they'll find him soon.

613
00:36:38,070 --> 00:36:40,656
-Jeong-suk.
-Why did you leave him alone?

614
00:36:40,740 --> 00:36:43,117
I stepped out for a minute
to get him popcorn.

615
00:36:43,618 --> 00:36:46,662
I didn't think he'd disappear
in that short amount of time.

616
00:36:50,583 --> 00:36:53,794
You never know anything.

617
00:36:55,129 --> 00:36:57,965
