624
00:37:09,685 --> 00:37:11,562
How did it happen?

625
00:37:11,646 --> 00:37:15,107
Min-ho said he wanted popcorn.
I told him to wait there.

626
00:37:15,191 --> 00:37:16,275
-You told him to wait?
-Yes!

627
00:37:16,359 --> 00:37:18,569
-Did you say it clearly?
-I did.

628
00:37:18,653 --> 00:37:20,071
-And?
-He was gone when I returned.

629
00:37:20,154 --> 00:37:21,948
You're here for the missing child?

630
00:37:22,031 --> 00:37:24,033
-Yes.
-Where would he go?

631
00:37:24,116 --> 00:37:25,284
The mother's over there.

632
00:37:25,368 --> 00:37:26,953
-Did you search the area?
-I did.

633
00:37:27,036 --> 00:37:29,080
Try and think where he could be once more.

634
00:37:29,163 --> 00:37:30,122
Where can he be?

635
00:37:30,206 --> 00:37:33,501
Did you search the whole area?
You double-checked?

636
00:37:35,962 --> 00:37:38,214
You already checked
all the places he might be?

637
00:37:38,839 --> 00:37:39,674
Yes.

638
00:37:39,757 --> 00:37:42,134
I went to all his usual hangouts.

639
00:37:42,927 --> 00:37:46,430
Then, let's do another search
in the theater area

640
00:37:46,514 --> 00:37:48,266
where he disappeared.

641
00:37:49,141 --> 00:37:51,143
He could be waiting there.

642
00:37:52,812 --> 00:37:56,023
He's never been anywhere alone
besides school and home.

643
00:37:58,484 --> 00:38:01,862
It's so dark out. He must be terrified.

644
00:38:03,447 --> 00:38:04,699
He must be so cold.

645
00:38:08,369 --> 00:38:10,121
I used to live in the US.

646
00:38:10,746 --> 00:38:13,332
There's a big amusement park
called Disneyland there.

647
00:38:15,209 --> 00:38:17,878
This town is smaller than the park.

648
00:38:19,714 --> 00:38:21,632
I'm saying we'll find him soon.

649
00:38:33,894 --> 00:38:36,981
Wait! That's my mother.

650
00:38:45,740 --> 00:38:47,199
Mom!

651
00:38:54,623 --> 00:38:56,667
I got a call from In-tae.

652
00:38:57,793 --> 00:38:59,628
How could this happen?

653
00:38:59,712 --> 00:39:02,298
I'm looking for him
with a detective right now.

654
00:39:02,381 --> 00:39:04,884
