selling such vulgar things!

663
00:39:28,115 --> 00:39:29,992
It makes me tremble.

664
00:39:31,577 --> 00:39:33,079
Mom.

665
00:39:33,162 --> 00:39:36,332
You may be mad for money,
but you've crossed the line.

666
00:39:36,415 --> 00:39:40,961
What do you even get
by doing that to make money?

667
00:39:41,462 --> 00:39:44,006
A mother should act like one.

668
00:39:45,257 --> 00:39:47,259
Don't you have any shame?

669
00:39:51,180 --> 00:39:52,264
What about you?

670
00:39:55,017 --> 00:39:57,144
Do you think you're acting like a mother?

671
00:39:58,354 --> 00:40:00,981
-What?
-I'm going crazy as is.

672
00:40:01,690 --> 00:40:04,402
And you're hurting me
even more with your harsh words.

673
00:40:04,485 --> 00:40:06,195
Is that acting like a mother?

674
00:40:06,904 --> 00:40:08,781
You should be ashamed of yourself!

675
00:40:16,497 --> 00:40:18,416
Min-ho!

676
00:40:21,335 --> 00:40:22,795
Kwon Min-ho!

677
00:40:25,548 --> 00:40:27,258
Min-ho!

678
00:40:43,232 --> 00:40:44,442
Are you all right?

679
00:40:45,276 --> 00:40:47,236
Yes. Let's go before it's too late.

680
00:40:59,373 --> 00:41:00,374
Min-ho.

681
00:41:02,751 --> 00:41:04,211
Min-ho!

682
00:41:04,295 --> 00:41:06,964
Ms. Han, you go that way
and I'll go this way.

683
00:41:07,047 --> 00:41:08,048
Okay.

684
00:41:11,844 --> 00:41:12,845
Min-ho.

685
00:41:15,764 --> 00:41:16,765
Min-ho.

686
00:41:37,578 --> 00:41:38,621
Min-ho.

687
00:41:41,290 --> 00:41:42,583
Min-ho.

688
00:41:44,084 --> 00:41:45,085
Min-ho.

689
00:41:47,046 --> 00:41:48,255
Min-ho.

690
00:41:55,262 --> 00:41:56,472
Min-ho!

691
00:42:03,020 --> 00:42:04,063
Min-ho.

692
00:42:06,815 --> 00:42:08,400
-Can I ask you a question?
-Sure.

693
00:42:08,484 --> 00:42:11,320
Have you seen a boy this tall,
around eight years old?

694
00:42:21,413 --> 00:42:22,706
Min-ho!

695
00:42:23,290 --> 00:42:24,333
Min-ho!

696
00:42:26,752 --> 00:42:27,795
Min-ho!

697
00:42:29,421 --> 00:42:30,381
Min-ho.

698
00:42:32,967 --> 00:42:34,134
