GEUMJE GOCHUJANG

711
00:43:42,369 --> 00:43:43,370
Min-ho!

712
00:43:44,204 --> 00:43:45,497
Min-ho!

713
00:43:45,581 --> 00:43:46,707
Mom.

714
00:43:47,499 --> 00:43:50,794
What are you doing here?
I've been looking all over for you.

715
00:43:53,172 --> 00:43:56,592
My goodness, you're cold as ice!

716
00:43:56,675 --> 00:43:57,968
