743
00:46:28,827 --> 00:46:30,037
Really…

744
00:46:32,206 --> 00:46:33,790
thank you so much.

745
00:47:31,890 --> 00:47:33,225
NANA BAND

746
00:47:57,583 --> 00:47:59,918
