756
00:48:25,027 --> 00:48:28,322
No. I'm going to walk with Dong-u.

757
00:48:29,990 --> 00:48:30,991
Look at me.

758
00:48:32,576 --> 00:48:34,870
Then come straight home, okay?

759
00:48:34,953 --> 00:48:37,623
Don't go somewhere else
without telling me ever again.

760
00:48:38,915 --> 00:48:40,250
I really won't.

761
00:48:41,668 --> 00:48:42,586
I'm going now.

762
00:48:42,669 --> 00:48:44,504
Here, take this.

763
00:48:44,588 --> 00:48:46,840
Have a good day and come straight home!

764
00:48:51,261 --> 00:48:53,013
Greet people politely.

765
00:48:53,096 --> 00:48:54,056
-Okay.
-Go.

766
00:49:03,774 --> 00:49:06,902
I almost forgot! Today is…

767
00:49:18,705 --> 00:49:19,706
Oh, my.

768
00:49:20,374 --> 00:49:23,001
It's been a long time
since I got paid a salary.

769
00:49:23,877 --> 00:49:26,088
It's more than I expected.

770
00:49:26,171 --> 00:49:27,172
I know.

771
00:49:28,590 --> 00:49:29,591
That's it?

772
00:49:31,593 --> 00:49:33,261
When money comes in,

773
00:49:33,345 --> 00:49:36,348
you have to welcome it passionately
to make even more money.

774
00:49:36,431 --> 00:49:37,974
Here, hold this.

775
00:49:39,017 --> 00:49:40,060
Okay.

776
00:49:40,644 --> 00:49:42,229
On the count of three,

777
00:49:42,312 --> 00:49:44,231
