778
00:49:44,314 --> 00:49:45,232
Holler? All right.

779
00:49:45,315 --> 00:49:46,900
One, two, three!

780
00:50:20,684 --> 00:50:21,852
Gosh.

781
00:50:22,686 --> 00:50:25,147
Didn't you hurt your back?

782
00:50:25,230 --> 00:50:28,191
