when we went up the stairs earlier.

783
00:50:29,151 --> 00:50:30,277
You're right.

784
00:50:30,777 --> 00:50:33,989
My goodness. I'm being totally honest.

785
00:50:34,072 --> 00:50:37,200
I think I was miraculously cured
the minute I saw this money.

786
00:50:38,910 --> 00:50:40,787
Anyway, what happened to your face?

787
00:50:41,747 --> 00:50:45,083
It's just a small scratch. It's nothing.

788
00:50:45,167 --> 00:50:46,293
Anyway,

789
00:50:47,502 --> 00:50:48,712
looking at this

790
00:50:49,463 --> 00:50:52,174
makes me forget all my troubles.

791
00:50:53,842 --> 00:50:56,762
