Go shopping.

793
00:51:04,686 --> 00:51:05,896
Shopping?

794
00:51:06,646 --> 00:51:07,481
Welcome.

795
00:51:07,564 --> 00:51:09,316
I'll take this one.

796
00:51:09,399 --> 00:51:10,817
This bag?

797
00:51:12,194 --> 00:51:13,695
-That's 28,000 won.
-Okay.

798
00:51:24,539 --> 00:51:26,416
-Thank you.
-Goodbye.

799
00:51:28,001 --> 00:51:31,421
-I'll take this one.
-Okay.

800
00:51:31,505 --> 00:51:33,799
It's for my daughter to study on.

801
00:51:33,882 --> 00:51:35,050
I see.

802
00:51:46,561 --> 00:51:48,021
Let's get shoes.

803
00:51:48,104 --> 00:51:48,980
Do you have a size…

804
00:51:49,064 --> 00:51:50,649
I'll take one pack of chwinamul.

805
00:51:53,527 --> 00:51:55,445
-How do I look?
-You look so pretty!

806
00:51:56,863 --> 00:51:57,697
Should I get them?

807
00:51:57,781 --> 00:51:59,616
I'll take three of those.

808
00:52:06,081 --> 00:52:07,374
Thank you.

809
00:52:08,542 --> 00:52:10,043
Thank you.

810
00:52:10,544 --> 00:52:11,670
Thank you.

811
00:52:21,179 --> 00:52:22,264
I'll pay.

812
00:52:41,408 --> 00:52:43,869
I gave you extra, so come back again!
Promise me!

813
00:52:44,369 --> 00:52:46,288
-Take a look.
-Next time.

814
00:52:46,371 --> 00:52:47,789
-Come next time.
-I will.

815
00:53:33,960 --> 00:53:36,880
Darling, I'm so thankful.

816
00:53:37,464 --> 00:53:38,590
Dad?

817
00:54:50,537 --> 00:54:52,580
What are you doing?

818
00:54:52,664 --> 00:54:54,249
Your home isn't around here.

819
00:54:55,750 --> 00:54:58,420
-Why did you come back?
-I worried you'd be like this.

820
00:55:01,297 --> 00:55:03,842
Dad should be the one hiding, not you.

821
00:55:13,393 --> 00:55:14,769
About before.

822
00:55:15,353 --> 00:55:16,604
I thought about it…

823
00:55:18,606 --> 00:55:21,609
and realized
I was your age when it happened.

824
00:55:34,122 --> 00:55:35,540
I was 32 years old.

825
00:55:36,374 --> 00:55:38,793
I still wanted to be loved.

826
00:55:38,877 --> 00:55:41,212
I wanted to be seen as attractive.

827
00:55:42,464 --> 00:55:45,759
Jeong-ho, what do you hope Dad will bring?

828
00:55:45,842 --> 00:55:48,803
Rubber shoes with the train logo. You?

829
00:55:48,887 --> 00:55:50,889
A bag of hard candy.

830
00:55:50,972 --> 00:55:54,100
Your dad's coming home after months.

831
00:55:54,184 --> 00:55:55,769
Are his gifts more important?

832
00:55:55,852 --> 00:55:58,229
Mom, don't you want anything?

833
00:55:58,313 --> 00:56:02,150
All I want is for your father
to return safe and sound.

834
00:56:02,650 --> 00:56:05,070
Making money in a place
where he doesn't know anyone

835
00:56:05,153 --> 00:56:06,946
must have been hard for him.

836
00:56:10,492 --> 00:56:11,785
Dad's home!

837
00:56:12,410 --> 00:56:13,620
-Dad!
-Dad!

838
00:56:16,539 --> 00:56:17,582
How have you been?

839
00:56:17,665 --> 00:56:18,750
Good.

840
00:56:21,086 --> 00:56:22,629
Come on in.

841
00:56:30,011 --> 00:56:32,597
After all that big talk
about making money in Seoul

842
00:56:32,680 --> 00:56:36,392
and not coming home empty-handed…

843
00:56:37,393 --> 00:56:41,564
I didn't think he meant
he'd be holding another woman's hand.

844
00:56:43,149 --> 00:56:48,238
It happened to quite a lot of women
back in the day.

845
00:56:49,280 --> 00:56:53,243
I tried to pull myself together.

846
00:56:57,789 --> 00:57:00,792
Mom, I have to pee.

847
00:57:04,796 --> 00:57:05,880
You have to pee?

848
00:57:14,472 --> 00:57:15,473
It's Dad.

849
00:57:18,017 --> 00:57:20,520
What's going on? Why are you so late?

850
00:57:20,603 --> 00:57:22,897
I told you already.

851
00:57:25,191 --> 00:57:29,028
Let's go inside. Did you miss me?

852
00:57:29,112 --> 00:57:30,113
Of course I did.

853
00:57:45,253 --> 00:57:47,213
I couldn't stop my heart

854
00:57:48,423 --> 00:57:50,216
from breaking into a million pieces.

855
00:57:54,012 --> 00:57:55,972
Could you wash this too?

856
00:57:56,055 --> 00:57:57,223
Ms. Lee?

857
00:57:59,017 --> 00:58:00,894
How dare she, in my house?

858
00:58:00,977 --> 00:58:03,062
And on top of my children's clothes?

859
00:58:03,646 --> 00:58:05,857
I lost it for a moment.

860
00:58:10,653 --> 00:58:12,030
Are you insane?

861
00:58:14,073 --> 00:58:14,908
Hey!

862
00:58:14,991 --> 00:58:17,410
-Let go!
-Come on!

863
00:58:17,494 --> 00:58:19,913
You let go first, you crazy bitch!

864
00:58:19,996 --> 00:58:21,456
What the hell are you doing?

865
00:58:24,959 --> 00:58:26,169
Are you all right?

866
00:58:26,961 --> 00:58:28,505
Let me see.

867
00:58:28,588 --> 00:58:30,131
Yong-deok.

868
00:58:36,137 --> 00:58:38,681
Don't cry. Let's go in first.

869
00:58:38,765 --> 00:58:40,266
Don't cry, okay?

870
00:58:48,191 --> 00:58:49,484
It's up here!

871
00:58:50,735 --> 00:58:51,653
Hey!

872
00:58:54,197 --> 00:58:55,865
Mom!

873
00:58:59,827 --> 00:59:00,870
Mom.

874
00:59:01,704 --> 00:59:02,664
Let's go.

875
00:59:11,881 --> 00:59:14,217
Mom, why are you going this way?

876
00:59:14,300 --> 00:59:15,385
Aren't we going home?

877
00:59:16,302 --> 00:59:19,013
That's not our home anymore.

878
00:59:20,431 --> 00:59:22,392
The three of us will live by ourselves.

879
00:59:26,813 --> 00:59:31,609
You know how I've lived after that
better than anyone.

880
00:59:32,360 --> 00:59:34,362
It's a path I chose.

881
00:59:35,738 --> 00:59:38,783
But whenever things got tough,
I felt angrier and more wronged

882
00:59:38,866 --> 00:59:40,702
than I normally did.

883
00:59:41,327 --> 00:59:43,121
Their blind lust

884
00:59:43,204 --> 00:59:46,958
ruined my life and my family.

885
00:59:49,002 --> 00:59:49,961
Mom.

886
00:59:50,795 --> 00:59:51,838
That's why

887
00:59:52,714 --> 00:59:54,549
I couldn't stand it

888
00:59:55,300 --> 00:59:58,845
when I found out my own daughter
was selling products

889
00:59:58,928 --> 01:00:00,471
a woman like her would wear.

890
01:00:03,349 --> 01:00:04,642
I know you.

891
01:00:05,727 --> 01:00:09,647
I know you're doing it to make ends meet.

892
01:00:16,613 --> 01:00:18,489
My pitiful baby.

893
01:00:19,657 --> 01:00:22,160
Whenever I'd say hurtful things to you,

894
01:00:22,869 --> 01:00:25,038
my heart broke into pieces.

895
01:00:27,790 --> 01:00:28,791
But…

896
01:00:30,877 --> 01:00:32,879
it was not easy to accept it.

897
01:00:42,555 --> 01:00:45,642
It's stopped raining.

898
01:00:46,684 --> 01:00:49,729
Min-ho must be waiting for you. Go home!

899
01:00:52,273 --> 01:00:53,608
Here.

900
01:00:55,026 --> 01:00:56,402
What's this?

901
01:00:56,486 --> 01:00:57,654
Today is payday.

902
01:00:57,737 --> 01:00:59,989
I thought about getting thermals
but got those instead.

903
01:01:04,786 --> 01:01:06,996
I'm too old for this.

904
01:01:07,080 --> 01:01:10,333
-I have no one to show it off to.
-It's not for anyone else to see!

905
01:01:10,833 --> 01:01:11,959
Wear it for yourself.

906
01:01:31,229 --> 01:01:32,397
Mom.

907
01:01:32,480 --> 01:01:34,816
Where did you go so suddenly?

908
01:01:36,234 --> 01:01:37,276
Nowhere really.

909
01:01:38,111 --> 01:01:39,404
Why do you have your bag on?

910
01:01:39,487 --> 01:01:40,863
Because I like it!

911
01:01:41,364 --> 01:01:43,825
I want tomorrow to come faster!

912
01:01:43,908 --> 01:01:45,368
I want to show Dong-u.

913
01:01:46,869 --> 01:01:47,829
Would you like some?

914
01:01:50,081 --> 01:01:51,249
You have them.

915
01:01:52,166 --> 01:01:53,918
I'll be back after washing the dishes.

916
01:02:13,271 --> 01:02:17,442
Deep down, I knew about Mom's pain.

917
01:02:25,283 --> 01:02:26,993
Your father's very drunk.

918
01:02:27,952 --> 01:02:29,162
Let's go inside.

919
01:02:32,874 --> 01:02:34,333
Ever since that woman came,

920
01:02:35,626 --> 01:02:37,754
Mom always looked exhausted.

921
01:02:57,940 --> 01:02:59,484
The sadness she bore

922
01:03:00,818 --> 01:03:04,405
looked so heavy,
even in the eyes of a child.

923
01:03:10,411 --> 01:03:11,662
DAESUNG STEAMED BUNS

924
01:03:11,746 --> 01:03:12,747
Jeong-suk.

925
01:03:13,414 --> 01:03:14,457
Here, have one.

926
01:03:17,543 --> 01:03:18,836
Mom, you're not having one?

927
01:03:20,880 --> 01:03:22,215
It's for you.

928
01:03:22,298 --> 01:03:24,050
Isn't that heavy?

929
01:03:24,133 --> 01:03:25,927
It's not heavy at all.

930
01:03:27,345 --> 01:03:30,681
We can buy rice
and the pastries you like with this.

931
01:03:30,765 --> 01:03:32,183
It's not heavy at all.

932
01:03:34,268 --> 01:03:35,228
It's tasty.

933
01:03:37,355 --> 01:03:38,898
Is it that good?

934
01:03:38,981 --> 01:03:41,526
-Yes.
-My goodness. Take your time.

935
01:03:41,609 --> 01:03:43,486
DON'T BE ANXIOUS
CONFESS AND FIND HOPE

936
01:03:43,569 --> 01:03:45,780
I believed her
when she said it wasn't heavy.

937
01:03:48,241 --> 01:03:51,077
No, now that I think about it,

938
01:03:52,703 --> 01:03:55,122
I think I wanted to believe so.

939
01:04:18,145 --> 01:04:21,399
Why did she spend money on this
when she's struggling herself?

940
01:04:40,167 --> 01:04:43,170
While I've believed
that she's fine since she's Mom,

941
01:04:44,297 --> 01:04:45,756
so much time has passed.

942
01:04:47,758 --> 01:04:50,845
She must have been
unimaginably lonely that whole time.

943
01:05:03,190 --> 01:05:04,650
Now that I'm a mother…

944
01:05:06,736 --> 01:05:08,112
it pains me terribly.

945
01:05:40,728 --> 01:05:43,022
A VIRTUOUS BUSINESS

946
01:05:43,689 --> 01:05:45,483
I think I found the culprit.

947
01:05:46,400 --> 01:05:47,735
Who is it?

948
01:05:47,818 --> 01:05:49,904
I'm planning to join you.

949
01:05:49,987 --> 01:05:51,656
-Yes, that's great!
-Yes.

950
01:05:51,739 --> 01:05:54,825
I think the four of us
can achieve great things.

951
01:05:54,909 --> 01:05:55,910
It's cool.

952
01:05:55,993 --> 01:05:58,704
-But what work do you do, Mom?
-What?

953
01:05:58,788 --> 01:06:01,457
"Fantasy Lingerie Survey."

954
01:06:02,041 --> 01:06:05,336
We're doing a survey
regarding our in-home sales.

955
01:06:05,419 --> 01:06:08,381
I thought she'd have
changed her mind by now.

956
01:06:08,464 --> 01:06:10,841
Shouldn't the town ladies
call a town meeting

957
01:06:10,925 --> 01:06:13,427
to force her to stop that business?

958
01:06:13,511 --> 01:06:14,595
What is she doing?

959
01:06:14,679 --> 01:06:15,888
"Close my business"?

960
01:06:15,972 --> 01:06:18,516
I won't. I can't!

